{"tid":1830760,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2警中槍身亡 房屋起火","createTime":"2020-01-20T01:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T01:24:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"24b7c015fb73297fc408464f17982ffa46905f27","tid":1830760,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T01:04:27.000Z","msg":"美國夏威夷檀香山發生槍擊案，2名警員中槍身亡。槍手據報之後將自己的住所縱火燒毀，火勢一度波及其他鄰居，附近居民需要疏散。估計槍手仍然在逃。<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地星期日下午，報道稱，警員接報處理一宗襲擊案時遇到一名持槍男子，並遭到槍擊。 警方在社交網站Twitter，向遇害警員的親友送上最深切的哀悼，但報道未有交代槍擊動機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503702-20200120.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503702-20200120.htm&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BPyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=1c034be6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503702-20200120.htm&h=ec52b34f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503702-20200120.htm</a>"},{"pid":"28e24daec25a2ea7dad9e688d2844ec7828f86cc","tid":1830760,"uid":38737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T01:05:11.000Z","msg":"點解唔係香港"},{"pid":"f4775728db653b1557aad9b9f843a2154a8a268a","tid":1830760,"uid":257527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T01:17:34.000Z","msg":"廢老口中的美國標準。<br />\n係會死差佬的。<br />\n<br />\n香港人太仁慈，死咁多人先換取，爆下缸"},{"pid":"2cdf40c553df862df2c8e00c5fb420fa7ff9fda4","tid":1830760,"uid":27700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T01:24:43.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等我仲開心咗陣！"}]}